{"tid":2121473,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫學會稱社區隔離設施飽和後需考慮方艙醫院模式收症","createTime":"2020-07-23T10:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T10:31:58.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3075063ba273fd53616fe2117830a160f0d7bf0","tid":2121473,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"醫學會稱社區隔離設施飽和後需考慮方艙醫院模式收症<br />\n2020-07-23 HKT 18:15<br />\n<br />\n&quot;醫學會會董陳以誠表示，醫管局的1700張隔離病床，3日前已經用了超過1200張，若每日繼續有超過100宗個案，鯉魚門渡假村的數百床位亦幫不了多少，相信不出數日便會超負荷，屆時可能要用武漢方艙醫院的方式，即安排病人在一間配備通風系統的大房間。至於選址方面，陳以誠認為，當局早前提出用作社區隔離設施的亞洲國際博覽館，是可以擺放過千床位、有洗手間、有通風系統的現成場地，又遠離民居，是可行的選址。 &quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539489-20200723.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539489-20200723.htm&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCIbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=54df1c9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539489-20200723.htm&h=4245da89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539489-20200723.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">Well said</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0897779ef347fbd905eb16dad19509b14949921f","tid":2121473,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:25:36.000Z","msg":"特首唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11d246cc599600280bdaa4d202a967e0cdedb78","tid":2121473,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ofCQKpU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FofCQKpU.jpg&h=54132f40&